OL,3,CBack on the ballot: Politicians
OL,4,Creinstate senators for next election
OL,6,FSenators will return to the Jersey
OL,7,FStates Assembly after politicians
OL,8,Fnarrowly decided to bring them back
OL,9,Ffrom the next election in 2026.
OL,11,FIt means candidates will again be able
OL,12,Fto stand for one of nine island-wide
OL,13,Froles which will replace a deputy in
OL,14,Feach district.
OL,16,FThe position was scrapped in 2022 and
OL,17,Fthere have been several unsuccessful
OL,18,Fattempts to reintroduce it until
OL,19,FDeputy Elaine Millar's proposition
OL,20,Fpassed by 25 votes to 20 with one
OL,21,Fabstention and one vote cast too late.
