OL,3,CBack on the ballot: Politicians
OL,4,Creinstate senators for next election
OL,6,FThe island's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FLyndon Farnham, says: "It's been a
OL,8,Flong, fairly tough and acrimonious
OL,9,Fdebate. I support the return of the
OL,10,Fisland-wide mandate because I firmly
OL,11,Fbelieve it's what the majority of
OL,12,Fislanders want and it's the fairest
OL,13,Fform of election in my opinion."
OL,15,FHowever, there is frustration from
OL,16,Fsome that so much time has been spent
OL,17,Ftalking about the political makeup of
OL,18,Fthe States, rather than issues
OL,19,Fdirectly facing islanders.
